        <abstract>
            <p>Illness of his son [Leonard]. Has done no work for weeks.</p>
            <p>JDH’s hybrid orchids are interesting; CD is surprised many hybrids are not produced.</p> 
<p>George [Darwin] caught a moth sucking <hi rend="italic">Gymnadenia conopsea</hi> with a pollen-mass of <hi rend="italic">Habenaria bifolia</hi> sticking to it.</p> 
